grade_preconditions.en:
The prerequisites for obtaining the final result of the course are:
1) all independent assignments have been submitted;
2) the assignments meet the substantive requirements given in separate instructions;
3) practical training and study visit(s) have been completed;
4) active and substantive participation in discussion seminars.

